A little story today. It goes like this. I drop by one of our teams, and within completely different discussion I get asked this very &ldquo;simple&rdquo; question:
&ldquo;Can we overlay an actual development team cost on top of product revenues so that we know if we are in the red or in the green?&rdquo;
If you haven&rsquo;t noticed yet, there&rsquo;s a flaw in this question. The problem is, it simply doesn&rsquo;t make sense from economic point of view.
